  <li id="comment-40640" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Christine M.</cite></div>
      <a href="index.html?p=206#comment-40640"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-02-17T17:11:42-05:00">Monday, February 17, 2014 at 5:11 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Just when I think I can&#39;t possibly like you more, you come out as an angsty NIN fan.  I was a few years behind you- The Fragile (left) was on repeat for a good year. And I&#39;m also now called &#8220;grandma&#8221; by my friends for my un-ironic preference to crochet at home with tea or straight bourbon (or both) on a Friday night. I would&#39;ve loved banana bread on V-day. 🙂</p>
<p>The curd looks so easy! Can&#39;t wait to try it.</p>
    </div>

