    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I share your love of lime curd after having made &#8220;curds&#8221; from a variety of citrus &#8211; ruby red grapefruit, meyer lemon, blood orange, lime, and plain old lemon.  The late Madelene Hill introduced me to the concept when I worked with her, and savoring that memory adds to my enjoyment.</p>
    </div>

